  "text": "T [CITATION_1] were also selected for field experiments due to their potential to enhance the growth of various plants [CITATION_2] and the high ability to produce PQQ [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] , respectively, although they did not show a growth promotion effect in the screening. It is of note that we did not observe any correlation between PQQ productivity of the cells cultured in vitro [CITATION_6] and the rice seedling growth in this study (data not shown). ",
